hold</strong> option and move the Threshold slider to specify a threshold v=
alue that achieves a good segmentation of the lungs. Click <strong class=3D=
"emphasis bold">Create Mask</strong> to accept the thresholding and return =
the Segmentation tab.</p><div class=3D"informalfigure"><div id=3D"d126e2937=
