imshow(maskedImageXZ)</pre></div></div></div><div class=3D"informalfigure">=
<div id=3D"d126e29437" class=3D"mediaobject"><p><img src=3D"https://ww2.mat=
hworks.cn/help/releases/R2023b/examples/images/win64/SegmentLungsFrom3DChes=
tScanExample_05.png" width=3D"302"></p></div></div><h3 class=3D"title" id=
=3D"SegmentLungsFrom3DChestScanExample-3">Create Seed Mask and Segment Lung=
s Using activecontour</h3><p>Create the 3-D seed mask that you can use with=
 the <code class=3D"literal">activecontour</code> function to segment the l=
ungs. </p><p>Create a logical 3-D volume the same size as the input volume =
and insert <code class=3D"literal">mask_XY</code> and <code class=3D"litera=
l">mask_XZ</code> at the appropriate spatial locations.</p><div class=3D"co=
de_responsive -has_code_copy"><div class=3D"programlisting"><div class=3D"c=
odeinput"><div class=3D"btn-group code_actions"> <button type=3D"button" cl=
ass=3D"btn btn-default dropdown-toggle" data-toggle=3D"dropdown" aria-haspo=
pup=3D"true" aria-expanded=3D"false"> <span class=3D"copy_code_popover_targ=
et" id=3D"copy_popover_09"><span class=3D"icon-copy" id=3D"copy_popover_09"=
