rue" class=3D"divider"></li><li class=3D"copy_code_openexample"><p><span cl=
ass=3D"icon-webinar"></span> Copy openExample Command<br><small>Paste comma=
nd in MATLAB to download and open example files</small></p><div role=3D"pre=
sentation" class=3D"input-group"><input type=3D"text" class=3D"form-control=
