mple"><p><span class=3D"icon-webinar"></span> Copy openExample Command<br><=
small>Paste command in MATLAB to download and open example files</small></p=
><div role=3D"presentation" class=3D"input-group"><input type=3D"text" clas=
s=3D"form-control" readonly=3D"" value=3D"openExample('images/SegmentLungsF=
rom3DChestScanExample')"><span class=3D"input-group-btn"><button class=3D"b=
